/><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：種族清洗 香港人，仲唔反佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851323</a>"},{"pid":"50ba5e120fde14ba6b92a7fcbef894b58ddecb68","tid":1851583,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cf3665610e858030cab24c50b6b3afb70aabcbe","tid":1851583,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"雖然政府都係廢<br />\n但起碼冇借口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"唔好亂帶風向<br />\n將抗疫結合抗爭唔得嘅"},{"pid":"04002604d056077a2bc4c1232a5eb6bd9bf381f7","tid":1851583,"uid":111541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f31062ae324fec0f6a0490cbf5ae075b4c20835","tid":1851583,"uid":41873,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"我宣布我屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我都宣布我屌樓主老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"36a2e5e09379e1ac452415b001d0942fdd3b6f09","tid":1851583,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"要休息"},{"pid":"970e0118d8b29cfd75b97fbb6b8e3abf762f6388","tid":1851583,"uid":68493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:55:02.000Z","msg":"我正式宣佈屌你老母"},{"pid":"75174784aae9e7e597f4dc64a2e49b98bb85edd8","tid":1851583,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"一早暫停左"},{"pid":"4f735cc90f7bffde8ab57639bd71ef827108020a","tid":1851583,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"三罷咪即係抗爭囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府一日唔全面封關，只會鼓勵更多疫區感染者衝入香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死更多人，<span style=\"color: gold;\">現全體香港市民要求將所有口岸（包括機場、羅湖、落馬洲、深圳灣、港珠澳大橋）全面禁止來自中國大陸旅客入境香港，否則繼續三罷！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">備注：<br />\n1.）非中國大陸旅客（包括台灣）可以正常入境香港<br />\n2.）擁有香港永久性居民身分可以正常入境香港<br />\n3.）任何人經中國大陸入境香港必須接受為期14日隔離及醫學監察</span>"},{"pid":"fa6f09f9aeca992b1344ed6701d45d763baa7a6c","tid":1851583,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f31062ae324fec0f6a0490cbf5ae075b4c20835","tid":1851583,"uid":41873,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"我宣布我屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"跟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我宣布我屌樓主老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"33e79ff61d10b09b9bb3d3b22c6c675830c1173a","tid":1851583,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:55:54.000Z","